title: DDFP 367: Sheky Awards preview
itunes:title: DDFP 367: Sheky Awards preview
description:
Shek and Handsome Hank discuss which NFL teams and cities are the most attractive to players. The guys then debate the best movie action star of all time, open listener mail and check in on the 2015 Sheky Awards. 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
